:: P01 [Passage]
He hears a breath that isn’t his. The attic holds it like a secret you don’t deserve.

<div class="dialogue">
<<if visited("P01") <= 1>>
"You picked a bad night to haunt me."
<<else>>
"You again. Thought the dust would bury the trail you keep making back here."
<</if>>
</div>

<div class="dialogue">
"Don’t fix me. Just witness. If you can bear that."
</div>

<<timedprogressbar $timer>>
  <<goto "P03">>
<</timedprogressbar>>

[[Act: Stay|P02]]
<<if $anger > 40 || $stress > 50>>[[Act: Look away|P05]]<</if>>



:: P02 [Passage]
<div class="dialogue">
"Alright. Terms are simple—no rescue missions. I talk; you stand there and try not to look holy."
</div>

<<timedprogressbar $timer>>
  <<goto "P03">>
<</timedprogressbar>>

[[Act: Nod once|P04]]
<<if $stress > 50 || $anger > 40>>[[Act: Stare too long|P05]]<</if>>



:: P03 [Passage]
<<set $stress = Math.max(0, Math.min(100, $stress + 3))>>

He searches your face for the verdict he swears is hiding there.

<div class="dialogue">
"Does this place disgust you? Or is it just me you can’t stand?"
</div>

<<if $stress > 70>>
  <<timedprogressbar $timer>>
    <<goto "P10">>
  <</timedprogressbar>>
<</if>>

<<if $stress >= 20 && $stress <= 60>>[[Act: Admit you're here|P06]]<</if>>
[[Act: Keep your distance|P05]]



:: P04 [Passage]
<<set $stress = Math.max(0, Math.min(100, $stress - 2))>>

