:: P05 [Passage]
<<set $anger = Math.max(0, Math.min(100, $anger + 6))>>

Your quiet hardens like a verdict. His shoulders rise; words turn sharp enough to bleed on.

<div class="dialogue">
"Don’t look at me like I’m a problem set. I’m not your homework."
</div>

<<if $anger > 60 || $stress > 80>>
  <<timedprogressbar $timer>>
    <<goto "P09">>
  <</timedprogressbar>>
<</if>>

[[Act: Lower your gaze|P11]]
[[Act: Soften stance|P04]]



